{"tid":1039162,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"重訓後，唔食碳水得唔得？","createTime":"2019-02-27T08:31:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T09:54:55.000Z","uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6f3380c0a19ea770c92816aec151762552a04bc6","tid":1039162,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T08:31:20.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n我早餐，午餐會食碳水，如粥、粉麵<br />\n而我做gym 多數係放工後 7pm-8:30pm <br />\n重訓完多數返屋企飲湯/食菜/魚/雞肉 （唔食飯) <br />\n對控制肥胖方面成效唔錯<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？"},{"pid":"8951c5195919131e4079bff2f0e362267245680c","tid":1039162,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T08:32:52.000Z","msg":"想知有冇巴打都係咁 ? <br />\n<br />\n雖然唔會好大隻<br />\n但一定唔會肥"},{"pid":"ec206b1e3b5c0abe35c5dc6970502aca9a2920b1","tid":1039162,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T08:33:57.000Z","msg":"有冇gym 佬入黎交流下"},{"pid":"4c90156559dbabc85fc85978df29ab0fddf7c85b","tid":1039162,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T08:34:43.000Z","msg":"晚餐唔食飯<br />\n只限早午餐食<br />\n真係易瘦好多"},{"pid":"8bbd6656c0ae53dc77d821bff6803525dc3baaf6","tid":1039162,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T08:42:19.000Z","msg":"因為營養學上<br />\n重訓後食碳水會幫助肌肉肥大合成 <br />\n正常黎講，重訓後係應要食飯 <br />\n<br />\n好可惜我只能晚上做gym <br />\n晚餐要gym後食<br />\n同時又唔想晚餐食飯 <br />\n<br />\n真係死症<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"066f8e60d86af6ada8a2a5d9509e935aa25e18ce","tid":1039162,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T08:43:28.000Z","msg":"食麵得唔得"},{"pid":"e0d33e1ad6d25211b8322104676b7e72bc589fc9","tid":1039162,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"066f8e60d86af6ada8a2a5d9509e935aa25e18ce","tid":1039162,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T08:43:28.000Z","msg":"食麵得唔得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T08:54:42.000Z","msg":"咪一樣<img src=\"